Description: Eren is free from the clutches of the Titans, but now he must learn to control a newly manifested power.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 13
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: In the not–too–distant future, a popular virtual reality video game traps its users, so the only way to log out is to beat the game. But if they die in the virtual world, it also means “game over” in the real world!
Title: SWORD ART ONLINE: AINCRAD, VOL. 2
Author: Reki Kawahara

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 4
Author: Okayado

Description: Issei Hyodo’s first date with Yuma Amano does not end well. Instead of a goodnight kiss, she kills him! But his death is only the beginning, when he is reincarnated as a devil.
Title: HIGH SCHOOL DXD, VOL. 2
Author: Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima
Contributor: by Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Max and the Flock continue their adventures in Antarctica with a group of environmental scientists who are studying the affects of global warming.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 8
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee

Description: Shion and Rat attempt to rescue Safu, who is imprisoned on the top floor of the Correctional Facility, which just happens to be filled with corpses missing their brains.
Title: NO. 6, VOL. 8
Author: Atsuko Asano

Description: Mei Tachibana has no friends and that’s how she likes it. But will she change her tune when Yamato, the most popular boy in school, wants to be her boyfriend?
Title: SAY I LOVE YOU, VOL. 3
Author: Kanae Hazuki

Description: The origins of the Survey Corps leaders Levi and Erwin are told in this spin–off series.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN: NO REGRETS, VOL. 1
Author: Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama
Contributor: by Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, the Titans attack and one of them goes rogue.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 2
Author: Hajime Isayama
